  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA57">
<l>polintiruṇṭa kārvāṉiṉ miṉṉēpōṟ ṟōṉṟi</l>
<l>malintu tiruvirunta mārpaṉ – polintu</l>
<l>karuṭaṉmēṟ koṇṭa kariyāṉ kaḻalē</l>
<l>teruṭaṉmēṟ kaṇṭāy teḷi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ankleted [feet] of the one on whose chest Śrī is joyfully sitting,</l>
<l>appearing like lightning among the ample darkening rain clouds,</l>
<l>[the feet] of the black one whom Garuḍa has grandly taken upon himself,</l>
<l>in [your] perception  see [them] clearly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
